messages.message:
@Serena I am facing a similar problem with cypress where my PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/60881) is a week old and the cypress tests fail due to license being expired. I have tried the following:
1. Updated to latest master
2. Deleted the Crafting sandbox and reran cypress
Can you pls help?
Last cypress run - https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/13567

you are correct that the tests are failing bc the license expired bc the PR is >1 week old

unfortunately, for now, the solution is to ask @Xindi Xu to manually extend the license https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_YIkXbxu7NE9FD5SQlJs5qj114LD-6yK__-qMA3sWis/edit?pli=1
Thanks for the help guys! Reran Cypress, hopefully they pass this time.
